➜大爱救心菜 人家有真爱——救心菜露酒义卖救助菜农重病孙子
http://www.sohu.com/a/282750569_528362	47716
<p class="ql-align-justify">近日，为给6岁孙子治病，近60岁的姜金库从商丘把自己种的白萝卜拉到孙子在郑州治病的医院附近卖，不少市民听说后纷纷伸出援手的新闻刷爆了朋友圈。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181218/6d485dfa020f49168c0eec01a40980f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181218/64475cd3911d45e6971a75989042fb3c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181218/e1f991ac3b0945ca9f58d8190197d59d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181218/1aac521e2df14fe9bbaf320751d360e1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">尉氏县瑞针蔬菜专业种植合作社负责人罗宣利知晓后，遂决定将救心菜露酒进行义卖，义卖的款项将全部捐献给姜金库救助重病孙子。<strong>（本报记者 师志强）</strong></p>